comments.content:
I was using the Enumclaw Starbucks every day for a week recently. I was so happy that a city with a name like that would have a Starbucks. I would have had big-time internet withdrawals if it weren’t for that hotspot. Very pretty area.

You’ll probably recognize some of the photos I took around there:  
 [http://www.fontplay.com/freephotos/landscape.htm](http://web.archive.org/web/20070808072851/http:/www.fontplay.com/freephotos/landscape.htm "http://www.fontplay.com/freephotos/landscape.htm")

The three on the right of the fifth row down are a little lake I walked around there.
